37b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 481}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "多地二手房业主抱团保卫房价，杭州有业主喊话邻居不要再贱卖自己的房子，建议上调 1 万 +，如何看待此事？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "「万物复苏，二手楼市启动，请不要再贱卖自己房子，建议在原来的基础上，向上调整 1 万 +。」 近日，有网友爆料，杭州市西湖区融创河滨之城小区业主群发以上消息。 3 月 6 日，《每日经济新闻》记者从该小区附近多家房产中介公司了解到，业主喊话邻居「不要贱卖房子」的行为的确存在。 中指研究院华东分院常务副总经理高院生认为，现阶段，杭州二手房市场的挂牌量大，此类行为不会对市场大环境产生太大波澜，「小范围捂住房源不卖，试图抬高房价的做法没有可行性。毕竟转售二手房是个人行为，而市场房源非常充足。」「建议上调 1 万 +，请不要再贱卖自己的房子！」多地二手房业主抱团「保卫房价」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-8f289d6a2c44ef14545a240633088c3b_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "442 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/588022562"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ir8/bxo60sdAuEAMaCDkyOTUzNTA2IIyamqAGMCw4rAdAAnIJNTg4MDIyNTYyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1678212473.2489495", "card_id": "Q_588062529", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 139}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待因 LPL 解说记得离职引发骆歆对昔日「老二」事件的追讨？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-9de045d85a9755c76e7ca17d8a384b1a_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "354 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/588062529"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ir8/bxo60sdAuEAMaCDkyOTYyMzQ0IPOzm6AGMAE40gFAA3IJNTg4MDYyNTI5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1678212473.249503", "card_id": "Q_586667576", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 302}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "更加自律的 C 罗，为什么状态不如梅西？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-4585d2ba4f79c9b1bb30b9d1933f3c59_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "289 万热度", "font_colo