育资源共享，并基于学业大数据为不同学生量身定制学习建议和指导方案，提升编程教育普及效率和发展质量。 杨杰还建议，构建智慧学习支持环境。搭建国家编程教育云平台，推动与国家中小学智慧教育平台等各级各类教育公共服务平台间的数据融通，开发汇聚各类优质数字化编程教学资源，不断扩大覆盖范围和应用对象。全国政协委员杨杰：建议将编程上升为中小学主要学科课程 - 中新网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-ce4dbcda47f0abfe3be3fe5352866a6f_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "62 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/587886046"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIr8/bxo60sdAuEAMaCDkyOTIyOTkwIMHZlqAGMHo40gxAFXIJNTg3ODg2MDQ2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1678212473.2625594", "card_id": "Q_588163404", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 41}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "大学生，一个人吃饭，一个人去上课，独来独往真的好吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "#大学生#独来独往"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "61 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/588163404"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ir8/bxo60sdAuEAMaCDkyOTg0ODI0INv/nKAGMAA4LkAWcgk1ODgxNjM0MDR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1678212473.2630343", "card_id": "Q_581014547", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 134}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果见到小时候的自己，你会对他／她说什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "5